<style>
    .about-h2{
        color: #4285f4;
        font-size: 4.7rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .about-description{
        color: #b1b1b1;
        font-size: 20px;
        /* width: 41%; */
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 3%;
    }
    .skill-box{
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 4%;
        margin-top: 7.5%;
    }

    .skill-box span{
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .skill-box span:hover{
        transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
</style>
<h2 class="about-h2">About Me</h2>
<p class="about-description">
    I’m Ashuraj Srivastav, a Full Stack Developer from New Delhi, India, specializing in creating impactful web solutions. With a strong focus on back-end development, I build secure and efficient systems that power seamless user experiences.
    
    As a freelancer, I’ve delivered high-performing landing websites and innovative tools like a QR code-based Attendance System and a CRM Quotation Generator. I’m driven by curiosity, creativity, and a commitment to delivering meaningful results.
    
    Let’s connect and create something extraordinary!</p>
